txt: No legacy is so rich as honesty. #<Author:0x007f2798b7ad88>
Honesty is the fastest way to prevent a mistake from turning into a failure. #<Author:0x007f279a3ad9c8>
We know the truth, not only by the reason, but also by the heart. #<Author:0x007f279961db78>
There is nothing so strong or safe in an emergency of life as the simple truth. #<Author:0x007f2798be8928>
Integrity is telling myself the truth. And honesty is telling the truth to other people. #<Author:0x007f27abee2ee0>
Hope is like the sun, which, as we journey toward it, casts the shadow of our burden behind us. #<Author:0x007f279973ea20>
No matter how dark the moment, love and hope are always possible. #<Author:0x007f279ad971a0>
Happiness can be found in even the darkest of times, but only to those who remember to turn on the light. #<Author:0x007f279a8f50e8>
Expect to have hope rekindled. Expect your prayers to be answered in wondrous ways. The dry seasons do not last. The spring rains will come. #<Author:0x007f27996fb518>
Once you choose hope, anything's possible. #<Author:0x007f2798ad88d0>
Treat people as if they were what they ought to be, and you help them become what they are capable of being. #<Author:0x007f27993045b8>
The greatest leaders are not necessarily the ones who do the greatest things. They are the ones that inspire others to do great things. #<Author:0x007f2798b53558>
Leaders who win the respect of others are the ones who deliver more than they promise, not the ones who promise more than they can deliver. #<Author:0x007f27982006e0>
A leader is someone who demonstrates what's possible. #<Author:0x007f2798fd8f60>
Great things can be achieved by leading through wisdom, empathy, and integrityâ€”with no other agenda than humanity. #<Author:0x007f2798c3dc20>
Above everything else I've done, I've always said I've had more guts than I've got talent. #<Author:0x007f27989548b0>
